<P>
   MAJORETTES _ What has happened to the twirler? There was a time
when the mighty majorette, in her sassy sequins and pompommed
boots, was envied by campus coeds everywhere. Over the past two
decades, though, she has pretty much pranced off the football field
and into gymnasiums where competitions are held. (Sturrock, Palm
Beach Post). WITH PHOTOS. MOVED.
