   COXNET WHEELS 0504 _ Although only 30 years old, the Pontiac
Firebird Trans Am is absolutely antediluvian. In fact, it's
wonderfully primitive, in other words, intended to appeal to
enthusiasts in their 30s and 40s who have the means to make their
old memories come alive. (DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
