</P>
<P>
   SUZE-ORMAN (San Francisco) _ The reigning shaman and high
priestess of personal finance may be a famous author, a television
personality and a millionaire, but she's still one of us. Yes, Suze
Orman has the common touch and a modest lifestyle. The 47-year-old
Orman still drives an old BMW and lives in a small Oakland, Calif.,
home she bought when she was a waitress at the Buttercup Bakery in
Berkeley 20 years ago. By EDWARD IWATA.
