   SALTER-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ I don't know how they did it,
but I am convinced that long ago my parents implanted in me some
sort of time-delay computer chip. It is now going off. I decided
this the other day after uttering, ``Golly, Ned!'' I hadn't used
that expression in at least 40 years _ but my Mom does. By
STEPHANIE SALTER.
</P>
