himself to a nationwide audience as a fiscal conservative and a
social moderate. Each position creates problems for the governor.
By DAN LYNCH.
</P>
<P>
   WONG-COLUMN (Oakland, Calif.) _ My son is 16.5 years old. That
unremarkable fact gained relevance as I followed the news of the
Littleton school massacre. By WILLIAM WONG.
</P>
