   &UR; FOOD &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PAGE INCLUDES TWO COLOR PHOTOS.
</P>
<P>
   PERFECTLY POACHED: If you haven't considered poaching a chicken
since the days of mom's Bisquick dumplings, now's the time.
(Includes one 4-column color photo of a chicken being poached and
one 1-column color photo of Hainanese Chicken and Rice.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: RECIPES: Chicken in Balsamic Vinegar, Hainanese Chicken
and Rice.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: CYBERSPICE: After a winter of stews, roasts and heavy
soups, this may be the perfect time to dust off that wok and get
into some serious stir-fry.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: RECIPE: Stir-Fried Beef With Sweet Peppers in Oyster
Sauce.
