<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-04 16:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3956 &Cx1f; taf-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RAMPS-2TAKES-NYT &LR;      05-04 0830
