<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS: New York Times is moving the following photos with
OKLA-STORMS and accompaning stories:
</P>
<P>
   (NYT12) MIDWEST CITY, Okla. -- May 4, 1999 -- OKLA-STORMS-5,
5-04 -- Toby Henry, 11, steps through what remains of his home on
Tuesday. (Michael Wyke/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT11) MOORE, Okla. -- May 4, 1999 -- OKLA-STORMS-4, 5-04 -- A
pedestrian walks past destroyed buildings on Tuesday. (Michael
Wyke/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT10) MIDWEST CITY, Okla. -- May 4, 1999 -- OKLA-STORMS-3,
5-04 -- Stacked cars and debris is all that is left of a Hampton
Inn hotel on Tuesday. (Michael Wyke/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
