   FBN-JAMAL _ Atlanta Falcons head coach Dan Reeves confirms that
Falcons tried to trade running back Jamal Anderson to New England
on draft day because of concerns about being able to resign him
after '99 season, when his current contract expires.
(Pasquarelli/Winkeljohn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 13.
