<HEADLINE>
REP. SWEENEY INTRODUCES AIRLINE COMPETITION LEGISLATION 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
