 &UR; GERON  &LR; _ &UR;  &LR; Geron, the company that found the ``immortality gene''
today acquired the Scottish company that owns the technology used
to clone Dolly the sheep. The deal is another coup for Menlo
Park-based Geron, which has kept pushing the biotech envelope. By
