price of his weekly airline ticket from Albany, N.Y., to
Washington, D.C., rise by 25 percent in recent weeks. So the New
York Republican has joined a growing number of lawmakers urging
Congress to increase airline competition in small- and medium-sized
cities. By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN. (Already filed.)
